uch a difference in other people‚Äôs lives by creating amazingly useful content that is 100% actionable. Also it may inspire mums to set up their own blog and to write about their experiences as a mother and a wife in the 21st century.</p><p><a href="http://www.miss-thrifty.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3139 lazyloaded" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-1024x544.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="544" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-1024x544.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-300x159.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-768x408.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-700x372.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty.jpg 1185w" data-ll-status="loaded" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3139" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-1024x544.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="544" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-1024x544.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-300x159.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-768x408.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty-700x372.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/missthrifty.jpg 1185w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="https://skintdad.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Skint Dad</a></h3><p>So when I talk about coming at a niche from a different angle, this example is exactly what I mean. Skint Dad is a site that helps young / new dads save money and be more frugal in their day to day living. There‚Äôs also a section on their that shows guys how to make a little more cash on top of their monthly day job wage, which is vital in some cases just to keep your head above water. &nbsp;A lot of new dads have the added stress of not having their wives‚Äô or girlfriends‚Äô wage coming in each month, due to&nbsp;the temporary career change in being a full time mum of a baby. So having some content around how they can make a few extra ‚ÄúPs‚Äù in their wallet each month, can ease the burden somewhat.</p><p><a href="http://skintdad.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3140 lazyloaded" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-1024x521.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="521" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-1024x521.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-300x153.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-768x391.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-700x356.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad.jpg 1221w" data-ll-status="loaded" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3140" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-1024x521.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="521" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-1024x521.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-300x153.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-768x391.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad-700x356.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/skintdad.jpg 1221w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 100px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h2 style="font-size: 27px; color: #46b5fb; text-align: center;"><strong>Examples of Entreprenurship Blogs</strong></h2><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="https://solopreneurhour.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SolopreneurHour.com</a></h3><p>A very well designed and slick blog that‚Äôs all about being your own boss and creating your own wealth. It‚Äôs a blog with a very active podcast feed. Their podcasts are insanely popular on itunes, and no doubt they make a fair bit of money from selling ad space on those podcasts. Podcasts is something to think about when creating your blog as it could be a great monetization tool.</p><p><a href="https://solopreneurhour.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3142 size-large lazyloaded" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur-1024x527.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="527" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur-1024x527.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur-300x154.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur-768x395.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur-700x360.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur.jpg 1200w" data-ll-status="loaded" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3142 size-large" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur-1024x527.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="527" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur-1024x527.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur-300x154.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/thesolopreneur-768x395.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsi