sitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/breakingintostartups-1024x471.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/breakingintostartups-300x138.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/breakingintostartups-768x353.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/breakingintostartups-700x322.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/breakingintostartups.jpg 1319w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 100px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h2 style="font-size: 26px; color: #46b5fb; text-align: center;"><strong>Examples of Tech Blogs</strong></h2><p>One of my favourite type of Blog is the ‚Äútech blog‚Äù. &nbsp;Now this isn‚Äôt something new to blog about, as Tech bloggers have been blogging about technology news and gadget reviews in detail online since the beginning of the internet, But because it‚Äôs such a vast niche, you could carve out yourself a really good angle within the tech blog sphere. The trick is to have your own take on tech and don‚Äôt just follow the trend. One area which hasn‚Äôt really been covered specifically is eco tech, so something to think about. Maybe a blog specifically covering tech aimed at becoming more environmentally conscious.</p><p>Anyway, here‚Äôs a few blogs&nbsp;in the tech niche that I really like and that I feel are doing something different and is thriving when it comes to organic traffic increases and revenue.</p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="https://knowtechie.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Knowtechie.com</a></h3><p><a href="https://knowtechie.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-3263" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20458'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1024" height="458" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-1024x458.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-300x134.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-768x343.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-700x313.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie.jpg 1228w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-1024x458.jpg" /><noscript><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-3263" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-1024x458.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="458" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-1024x458.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-300x134.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-768x343.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie-700x313.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/knowtechie.jpg 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><p>I‚Äôve been following this site since it started and has seen its progression from just one guy writing about stuff he loves, to a site that get‚Äôs decent traffic and has a team of writers.</p><p>Knowtechie is a great example of a site that started out as a hobby but has fast become a business. I like the angle they have as well. <strong>‚ÄúTech News For The Non Techie‚Äù.&nbsp;<em>KnowTechie</em> is a blog for people who love tech, but live outside the bubble.&nbsp;</strong>This is so refreshing, because so many tech blogs out there are a bit too technical and full to the brim of jargon. It‚Äôs nice to see a tech blog that has lowered the entry level to tech news.</p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 100px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3></h3><h2 style="font-size: 26px; color: #46b5fb; text-align: center;"><strong>Examples of Making Money Blogs</strong></h2><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><p>Like frugal blogs, making money related blogs have become insanely popular since&nbsp;the global economy has declined in recent years. The want for making more money in order to have a ‚ÄúOk‚Äù quality of life, is increasing year on year. Wages are not rising, jobs are becoming less secure and the cost of living is constantly rising. This is why sites like the ones below in this section are becoming more and more popular.</p><p>Again, if you come at this niche with a different angle, then potentially you can have a great and successful website on your hands.</p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="http://www.sidehustlenation.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SideHustleNation.com</a></h3><p>Side Hustle is an online community of entrepreneurs who‚Äôs goal is to gain <a href="https://freedomadvice.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">financial freedom</a> through creating businesses that can help them achieve that. There‚Äôs a collection of highly actionable blog posts on how to make additional income on top of your day job wage. They make good use of the podcast medium of content marketing by creating various podcasts with experts talking about a whole range of topics around entrepreneurship, <a href="https://makeawebsitehub.com/make-money-online-at-home/">making money online</a> and creating wealth.</p><p><a href="http://www.sidehustlenation.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3137" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20556'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1024" height="556" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-1024x556.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-300x163.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-768x417.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-700x380.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation.jpg 1152w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-1024x556.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3137" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-1024x556.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="556" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-1024x556.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-300x163.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-768x417.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation-700x380.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/sidehustlenation.jpg 1152w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="http://mywifequitherjob.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MyWifeQuitHerJob.com</a></h3><p>A great site, which is highly useful and inspirational for people wanting to change their 9 to 5 lives for something that will allow them to live a little and spend more time with the family. The site is really simple, and something you could build yourself on WordPress in a matter of day, but the content is where this site excels. Podcasts, tools, tutorials and blog posts that target a specific niche is where this guy makes his money. His podcasts are really popular and when you have content that gets a lot of ears and eyes to it, then so will the advertising income.</p><p>It‚Äôs the same with written content. If you have a popular page that get‚Äôs tens of thousands of views a month, then potentially you can sell ad space on those pages for hundreds of dollars a month, if not more.</p><p><a href="http://mywifequitherjob.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3138" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20533'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1024" height="533" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-1024x533.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-300x156.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-768x400.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-700x364.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob.jpg 1178w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-1024x533.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3138" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-1024x533.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="533" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-1024x533.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-300x156.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-768x400.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob-700x364.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mywifequitherjob.jpg 1178w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 100px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h2 style="font-size: 26px; color: #46b5fb; text-align: center;"><strong>Examples of Mommy Blogs</strong></h2><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><p>Mommy blogs are blog that are targeted towards parents, particularly women. Here‚Äôs my pick on the best mommy blog examples that I think are worth looking at. They offer information that‚Äôs resourceful and that can make parenthood that little bit easier. Most are monetised by sponsored post and display ads.</p><h3><a href="https://www.giovannafletcher.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GiovannaFletcher.com</a></h3><p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6091" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201000%20428'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1000" height="428" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher.jpg 1000w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher-300x128.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher-768x329.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher-140x60.jpg 140w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6091" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="428" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher.jpg 1000w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher-300x128.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher-768x329.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/givanna-fletcher-140x60.jpg 140w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></noscript></p><p>Giovanna is a writer, blogger, vlogger and mum. Her blog content is mainly about her life as a mother and a wife. She hosts a very popular podcast called <a href="https://www.giovannafletcher.com/podcasts/series-three" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Happy Mum, Happy Baby Podcast.</a></p><p>I love the variety of content on her blog. She mixes it up between informative blog posts about family life, what‚Äôs going on in her world and tips for mums and a really cool podcasts that cover a variety of subjects to do with parenting and being a mum. The fact that she‚Äôs not really hard selling at all is refreshing.</p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="http://cupofjo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CupOfJo.com</a></h3><p>One of the best mommy bloggers around, Joanna has a really simple looking blog, full to the brim of useful stuff for old and new mothers alike. What I love about this site is the simplicity of the theme, the really current design features and the typography. The <a href="https://makeawebsitehub.com/blog-ideas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">blog post ideas</a> are really clever as well and sets Jo‚Äôs site apart from all the other mommy bloggers.</p><p><a href="http://cupofjo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3143" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20604'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1024" height="604" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-1024x604.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-300x177.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-768x453.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-700x413.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo.jpg 1059w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-1024x604.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3143" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-1024x604.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="604" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-1024x604.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-300x177.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-768x453.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo-700x413.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/cupofjo.jpg 1059w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="http://bitofmomsense.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bit&nbsp;of Momsense</a></h3><p>Another well thought out and well designed mommy blog.&nbsp;This blog is quite varied in its content as its got a little bit of everything. If you love all things&nbsp;parenting, cooking with kids, craft with the children, health, family travel, stories, charity etc. then this site will give you plenty of inspiration on how you could start your own mommy blog.</p><p><a href="http://bitofmomsense.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3145" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20523'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1024" height="523" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-1024x523.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-300x153.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-768x392.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-700x357.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense.jpg 1252w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-1024x523.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3145" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-1024x523.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="523" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-1024x523.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-300x153.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-768x392.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense-700x357.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/momsense.jpg 1252w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="http://www.motherhooddiaries.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">motherhooddiaries.com</a></h3><p>Motherhood Diaries is an online parenting platform where parents and parents-to-be can share their opinions, expertise and solutions on all topics related to pregnancy and parenting. Leyla, who owns and maintains MHD, builds her traffic through targeting specific keywords related to parenting and creating resources around those phrases. She‚Äôs also concentrating her efforts on social channels like Pinterest and Facebook to create lucrative audiences via an alternative traffic source to Google.</p><p><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3503" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20544'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1024" height="544" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-1024x544.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-300x159.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-768x408.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-700x372.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries.jpg 1187w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-1024x544.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3503" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-1024x544.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="544" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-1024x544.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-300x159.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-768x408.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries-700x372.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/motherhooddiaries.jpg 1187w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 100px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h2 style="font-size: 26px; color: #46b5fb; text-align: center;"><strong>Examples of Parenting Blogs</strong></h2><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="https://wetheparents.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">We The Parents</a></h3><p><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3763" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20564'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1024" height="564" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-1024x564.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-300x165.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-768x423.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-700x386.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-1024x564.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3763" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-1024x564.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="564" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-1024x564.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-300x165.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-768x423.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents-700x386.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/wetheparents.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></p><p>WeTheParents.org is one of my favorite parent blogs. Rather than getting Mom‚Äôs view or Dad‚Äôs opinion, you get both sides of the parenting story. The content is a real mixture, Neve, the Mom tends to write about empowering mom stuff whilst her husband, Keane, seems to be a big kid who spends his time playing with and reviewing kids toys.</p><p>The main goal of this blog is to make parents‚Äô lives easier by doing the research for them. It can be a pain trawling through Google and to find the best products, so this mom and dad team get geeky finding out which products are the best for the whole family. (And which gear is just a waste of money!)</p><p>The site is beautifully designed and quick to load. It‚Äôs a great example of a simple WordPress theme that‚Äôs been well customized.</p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 100px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h2 style="font-size: 26px; color: #46b5fb; text-align: center;">Examples of Adventure Blogs</h2><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="https://adventureblog.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Adventure Blog</a></h3><p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6092" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201000%20420'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1000" height="420" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog.jpg 1000w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog-300x126.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog-768x323.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog-143x60.jpg 143w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6092" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="420" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog.jpg 1000w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog-300x126.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog-768x323.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-adventure-blog-143x60.jpg 143w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></noscript></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 50px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h2 style="font-size: 26px; color: #46b5fb; text-align: center;">Examples of Food / Wine Blogs</h2><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="http://pinchofyum.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pinch Of Yum</a></h3><p>My favourite food blog is this one. I think the style, design and tone of voice is just top notch. Lindsay really has blogging down to a fine art, not just with the writing but also in knowing how to make money from blogging. I reckon she has a massive email list which she has built up over the years, that&nbsp;she can use to literally print money with. Targeting her email list with her latest blog posts, affiliate links, deals, offers, coupons will make her plenty of cash each month.</p><p>I love her blogger resources page as well. A clever way to inspire other bloggers to take the plunge and use what she uses to create a successful food blog.</p><p><a href="http://pinchofyum.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3135" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20516'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1024" height="516" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-1024x516.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-300x151.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-768x387.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-700x353.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum.jpg 1224w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-1024x516.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3135" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-1024x516.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="516" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-1024x516.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-300x151.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-768x387.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum-700x353.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/pinchofyum.jpg 1224w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_