monetization method she uses &nbsp;with this page&nbsp;‚ÄúWhat‚Äôs in My Kitchen? Utensils Edition.‚Äù She can easily add in Amazon affiliate links to earn income from this page, by recommending quality products that she uses on a daily basis.</p><p>This is a great example of an outstanding food niche blog. Think about what she‚Äôs doing well and take note.&nbsp;Mouth watering photos, clean and simple theme layout, well&nbsp;formatted and styled recipe pages, excellent writing, conversational tone, and relatable back stories to each post.</p><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><h3><a href="https://12x75.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">12√ó75</a></h3><p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5391" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201000%20220'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1000" height="220" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12x75.jpg 1000w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12x75-300x66.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12x75-768x169.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12x75.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5391" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12x75.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="220" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12x75.jpg 1000w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12x75-300x66.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12x75-768x169.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></noscript></p><p>12 By 75 is by far one fo my favourite wine blogs. It‚Äôs well written and the information you get access to is via one of the most influential wine traders in the business. There‚Äôs not many blogs out there that‚Äôs written in the sa