ative if you promote the right product or offer something different to the rest of the fitness blogs out there.</p><p>Below, I have added fitness blogs that do what they do incredibly well and examples that you can gain insights and inspiration from.</p><h3><a href="http://www.niashanks.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NiaShanks.com</a></h3><p><a href="http://niashanks.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3134" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20461'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1024" height="461" data-lazy-srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-1024x461.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-300x135.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-768x346.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-700x315.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks.jpg 1319w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-1024x461.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3134" src="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-1024x461.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="461" srcset="https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-1024x461.jpg 1024w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-300x135.jpg 300w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-768x346.jpg 768w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks-700x315.jpg 700w, https://makeawebsitehub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/niashanks.jpg 1319w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></a></p><p>A very popular fitness blog mainly targeted towards women, where there‚Äôs a positive encouragement of women of all shapes and sizes to get fit 